n for the working girls but there some shadier older guys hanging around who like to cat-call. OVERALL: We paid about 100 euro per night with breakfast included鈥攁 good value. If I were traveling with a family, I鈥檇 stay here again; it was a clean and friendly place. Otherwise, I鈥檇 stay at the new, chic Hotel de las Letras down the street again instead. 
